      About this item

      • TRENDY CRESCENT SHAPED: This causal crossbody sling bag is designed as a minimalist half-moon with roomy space, perfect for any occasion, daily use, travel, work,etc.
      • PERFECT CROSSBODY SIZE: 12''(L) x 3.5'' (W) x 6.5''( H), there is a main compartment and 2 open pockets inside can hold your daily necessities, cell phone, powerbank, keys, etc.
      • ADJUSTABLE SHOULDER STRAP: The shoulder strap is very easy to adjust to your comfortable length, the drop from 14.5" to 23.6". It can use as a fanny pack, crossbody bag or chest bag.
      • SMOOTH ZIPPER & STABLE STRAP: This crescent cross body bag is closed by convenient zipper, the upgraded shoulder strap will not break. It's also a great choice as a gift for friends and family.

          How customer reviews and ratings work

          Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

          To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
